			<div class="post-2096 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-financial-privacy tag-alternative-currencies tag-bank tag-banking tag-banking-regulation tag-bitcoin tag-business tag-central-bank tag-currency tag-digital-currencies tag-digital-gold-currencies tag-economics tag-electronic-commerce tag-electronic-money tag-financial tag-financial-freedom tag-financial-privacy tag-foreign-exchange-market tag-goldmoney tag-money tag-national-currency tag-payment-systems tag-paypal tag-pecunix tag-the-best tag-us-federal-reserve tag-webmoney post_box top" id="post-2096">
